Ikponmwosa Alex Idehen, better known as Gerian is a Nigerian born Singer, songwriter and performer. Gerian was born on the 11th of September, 1994 into the royal family of Benin City, Edo State. He spent his early life in the beautiful city of Benin, Edo State, where he, later on, moved to the Gambia to further his education. For as long as he can remember, music has been an integral part of his life. He describes his style of music as Afro-Pop, a genre with a blend of Afrobeat & Dancehall. He has two songs that are available on all streaming platforms titled Matter and Abena which are trending now on TikTok. Inspired by Fela  Anikulapo-Kuti, Fantan Mojah, Buju Banton, Youssou n’dour and many others. Gerian promises to impact life positively with his music. Instagram: @iamgerian
Twitter: @iamgerian